OL,3,CTourism in decline in Cumbria as
OL,4,Ccounty sees 14% drop since 2019
OL,6,FNew figures have highlighted the
OL,7,Fdecline of tourism in Cumbria with
OL,8,Fvisitor numbers down 14% compared to
OL,9,F2019.
OL,11,FThe statistics are produced from the
OL,12,FScarborough Tourism Economic Activity
OL,13,FMonitor, commonly known as 'STEAM' and
OL,14,Freleased by Cumbria Tourism in
OL,15,Fpartnership with Cumberland Council,
OL,16,FWestmorland & Furness Council and the
OL,17,FLake District National Park Authority.
OL,19,FAlso in comparison to 2019 the number
OL,20,Fof day visitors to Cumbria have fallen
OL,21,Fby 18%.
