OL,3,CTourism in decline in Cumbria as
OL,4,Ccounty sees 14% drop since 2019
OL,6,FWhat are some of the key statistics
OL,7,Fcompared to the previous 12 months?
OL,9,FPresident of Cumbria Tourism Jim
OL,10,FWalker says: "Cumbria's #4.6billion
OL,11,Ftourism and hospitality industry is
OL,12,Fmade up of hundreds of small
OL,13,Fbusinesses who make a huge
OL,14,Fcontribution to other sectors,
OL,15,Fincluding transport and the wider
OL,16,Fsupply chain.
OL,18,F"They also help to create the assets
OL,19,Fthat make Cumbria such a special place
OL,20,Fto live and work for our local
OL,21,Fcommunities.
