OL,3,CTourism in decline in Cumbria as
OL,4,Ccounty sees 14% drop since 2019
OL,6,F"However, this latest data clearly
OL,7,Fdemonstrates that - after the economic
OL,8,Fshock of the pandemic and subsequent
OL,9,Fgovernment policy changes around
OL,10,Fimmigration and taxation - long-term
OL,11,Frecovery is proving extremely
OL,12,Fchallenging for these vital visitor
OL,13,Feconomy businesses as they face
OL,14,Freduced visitor numbers coupled with
OL,15,Fincreasing costs.
OL,17,F"Ultimately, this means less
OL,18,Fprofitability and ability to employ
OL,19,Fand re-invest."
