OL,6,FIn Cumbria more than half of the
OL,7,Frevenue made from tourism comes from
OL,8,Fvisitors staying overnight in the
OL,9,Fcounty.
OL,11,FThe percentage of revenue generated
OL,12,Foutwith of the traditional summer
OL,13,Fmonths also increased from 38.9% in
OL,14,F2024 compared to 36.1% in 2023.
OL,16,FWhere do tourists spend their money in
OL,17,FCumbria?
