OL,6,FPresident of Cumbria Tourism Jim
OL,7,FWalker added: "Cumbria has a shared
OL,8,FDestination Management Plan, which
OL,9,Fpublic and private partners are
OL,10,Fcollectively ambitious to deliver,
OL,11,Fenabling sustainable growth for the
OL,12,Fbenefit of the whole of the whole of
OL,13,Fthe county and its communities.
OL,15,F"At the moment, a combination of the
OL,16,Fcost of living crisis and a series of
OL,17,Funlinked and uncoordinated national
OL,18,Fpolicy changes are seriously damaging
OL,19,Fbusiness profitability, the economy,
OL,20,Fjobs and therefore communities.
